{
  "page": "Lhorulu",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\">\n<div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\">\n<div style=\"position: relative; border: 1px solid lightgray\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Free_Cities.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Lhorulu is located in Free Cities\"><img alt=\"Lhorulu is located in Free Cities\" src=\"/images/thumb/a/a3/Free_Cities.png/300px-Free_Cities.png\" width=\"300\" height=\"417\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/a/a3/Free_Cities.png/450px-Free_Cities.png 1.5x, /images/a/a3/Free_Cities.png 2x\" /></a><div style=\"position: absolute; z-index: 2; top: 63.3%; left: 59.4%; height: 0; width: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"><div style=\"position: relative; text-align: center; left: -4px; top: -4px; width: 8px; font-size: 8px; z-index:100;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/8px-Red_pog.png\" title=\"Lhorulu\" width=\"8\" height=\"8\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/12px-Red_pog.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/16px-Red_pog.png 2x\" /></div><div style=\"font-size:&#160;%; line-height: 110%; z-index:90; position: relative; top: -1.5em; width: 6em; left: 0.5em; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"padding: 1px;\">Lhorulu</span></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"thumbcaption\">Western <a href=\"/index.php/Essos\" title=\"Essos\">Essos</a> and the location of the Lhorulu\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:352px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Lhorulu_Stu_Barnes.JPG\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/d/db/Lhorulu_Stu_Barnes.JPG/350px-Lhorulu_Stu_Barnes.JPG\" width=\"350\" height=\"228\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/d/db/Lhorulu_Stu_Barnes.JPG/525px-Lhorulu_Stu_Barnes.JPG 1.5x, /images/d/db/Lhorulu_Stu_Barnes.JPG 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Lhorulu_Stu_Barnes.JPG\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>The Lhorulu. © Fantasy Flight Games</div></div></div>\n<p>The <b>Lhorulu</b> is a river in western <a href=\"/index.php/Essos\" title=\"Essos\">Essos</a>. The <a href=\"/index.php/Rhoynar\" title=\"Rhoynar\">Rhoynar</a> consider it a daughter of the <a href=\"/index.php/Rhoyne\" title=\"Rhoyne\">Rhoyne</a> and nickname it the <b>Smiling Daughter</b>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd14.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd14.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> Its headwaters begin south of the <a href=\"/index.php/Flatlands\" title=\"Flatlands\">Flatlands</a> and the river flows southeast into the Rhoyne. The <a href=\"/index.php/Sorrows\" title=\"Sorrows\">Sorrows</a> sit at the confluence of the Lhorulu and the Rhoyne. Between the Lhorulu and <a href=\"/index.php/Dagger_Lake\" title=\"Dagger Lake\">Dagger Lake</a> are the <a href=\"/index.php/Golden_Fields\" title=\"Golden Fields\">Golden Fields</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtloiaf.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtloiaf.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd14.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd14.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lhorulu&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>South of there <a href=\"/index.php/Rhoyne\" title=\"Rhoyne\">the Mother</a> meets Lhorulu, the Smiling Daughter from the <a href=\"/index.php/Golden_Fields\" title=\"Golden Fields\">Golden Fields</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd14.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd14.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Yandry\" title=\"Yandry\">Yandry</a> to <a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\">Tyrion Lannister</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lhorulu&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd14.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd14.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd14.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd14.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\">1.2</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_14\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 14\">Chapter 14</a>, Tyrion IV.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtloiaf.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtloiaf.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Lands_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"The Lands of Ice and Fire\">The Lands of Ice and Fire</a></i>.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></d